name: Toucan You Can Survive!
description:
A simple in-browser Flappy-bird inspired endless jumper in which you are a Toucan that must jump its way through a sky filled with nasty snakes. 

This game was made for the FlappyJam.

CONTROLS:

  • SPACE - Jump
  • R - Reset

Sources used:

Pixel Adventure 2 by Pixel Frog (itch.io)

Magic Cliffs Environment by ansimuz (itch.io)
